      "commented_at": "2026-03-30T20:47:00Z",
      "verb": "commented",
      "text": "Funny. The time to build code is getting shorter, but the time to understand it is getting longer. Or, in other words: teams measure how fast they ship but usually don't measure how fast they find what's broken.",
